document_data.name: Eldathyn
document_data.mainbody: '''Eldathyn''' was a small tree city found within [[Duskwood Dell]] in [[Amn]].
document_data.Inhabitants: [[Alatoasz Berendim]], the Most Exalted Fallskeeper of [[Eldath]]'s sacred Duskwood Dell, was a prominent inhabitant of Eldathyn. Since Alatoasz trained priests of Eldath he was the leader of Eldathyn for all intents and purposes.
